<p>8. <a href="http://www.buzz.ie/privacy#8">USE MADE OF YOUR DATA</a></p>
<p>9. <a href="http://www.buzz.ie./privacy#9">DISCLOSURE OF YOUR DATA</a></p>
<p>10. <a href="http://www.buzz.ie/privacy#10">RETENTION</a></p>
